data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT!! Do not miss your chance to make this Amazing and Rare property, HOME. Country Living and close to it all! Welcome Home to this Amazing 2 Story, 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath Farmhouse with 2296sqft of living space and 3.18 acres. The beautiful wrap around porch, mature trees and above ground pool say let the summer fun begin! Beautiful entry way to welcome family and friends. The Great Room has a wood burning fireplace set with beautiful cedar and stone. The kitchen has all stainless steal appliances and a butcher block island. Large indoor laundry room for convenience. Large dining room and an additional family room off of the Kitchen add extra living space. All of the Bedrooms are on the 2nd floor, including an Amazing Owner Suite. This home is ready for your farm animals too. The Chicken coop, small animal enclosure are being left with the property. The drive up your beautiful tree lined private drive way is so peaceful. This property has it all and ready for Entertaining. Property is within minutes to shopping, schools and amenities. I-4 is just 5mins away for easy commute to Orlando or Tampa. You will fall in love with this beautiful Florida home with charm and land. As a BONUS, seller is offering $10,000 toward buyers pre-paids, closing cost or rate buy down. Do not wait to make this one of a kind Property your Home.
